 thousands of blogs and websites that they display your jobs within.</p>\n<p>The plugin creates a form to general the code, the Look &amp; feel of the widget can be customized by specifying the background and font/link color properties and many more options.</p>\n<p>The users can select ad listings&#8217; categories and/or a keyword to display its ads accordingly.Imagine the possibilities.</p>\n<p><strong>FeedPress for JobRoller</strong>  is packed with a PayPal donation option so you easily can monetize your website as you provide this as a free service (optional).</p>\n<p>Test it yourself <img src=\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/simple-smile.png\" alt=\":)\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<p><a class=\"btn green big\" style=\"width: 48%;float: left;margin: 5px;background: #58b35a;border: 1px solid #419f44\" href=\"http://demos.jobthemes.com/index.php=feedpress-jr-demo\" target=\"_blank\">Live Demo</a> <a class=\"btn green big\" style=\"width: 48%;float: left;margin: 5px;background: #58b35a;border: 1px solid #419f44\" href=\"http://demos.jobthemes.com/index.php=feedpress-jr-admin\" target=\"_blank\">Admin Demo</a></p>\n<hr style=\"background: none;border: none\" />\n<h2>Features:</h2>\n<p><strong>_For the admin (YOU):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>    RSS to Content converter</li>\n<li>    Display jobroller jobs on your Miltisites (appthemes or any other websites)</li>\n<li>    Promote your job board website</li>\n<li>    An option to display featured jobs only <span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong>[NEW]</strong></span></li>\n<li>    Limit how many listings to display per widget <span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong>[NEW]</strong></span></li>\n<li>    Extensive admin panel</li>\n<li>    Advanced or Basic mode</li>\n<li>    Donation ready (customizable options)</li>\n<li>    SEO: Place a clean link in the bottom of the widget to increase high quality backlinks</li>\n<li>    MU and Jobroller 1.7.5 compatible</li>\n<li>    Compatible with all JobRoller child themes.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>_For the users (Your website&#8217;s users):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>    Customize the widget with ease</li>\n<li>    Select job categories and/or keywords</li>\n<li>    Scrolling content or not</li>\n<li>    Horizontal or vertical scrolling <span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong>[NEW]</strong></span></li>\n<li>    Responsive widget option<span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong> [NEW]</strong></span></li>\n<li>    Set how many jobs to display in the widget <span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong>[NEW]</strong></span></li>\n<li>    Color schemes customizer</li>\n<li>    Size controller</li>\n<li>    8 Predefined styles</li>\n<li>    Live instant widget preview</li>\n<li>    Easy to use, no techies required</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>_How to use:</strong><br />\nIt’s really easy to use and can be up on your users&#8217; sites in minutes. Here are the three simple steps:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>    Set ad keyword and/or ad categories</li>\n<li>    Customize the display of the widget</li>\n<li>    Copy and paste the generated code into your web page</li>\n</ol>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Pre-sales questions</strong> | Post your questions in the comments tab, or simply drop us an email to: <a href=\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2015/02/supportjobthemes.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-9430 alignleft\" src=\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2015/02/supportjobthemes.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"161\" height=\"21\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #474747\"><strong>Dedicated support</strong> |</span> We take huge pride in our customer support and how it has differentiated us from the competition.We have a support team located 3 countries in just about every time zone and try our hardest to ensure support responses within 24 hours.</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #474747\"><b>Suggestions and Feedback | </b></span>Our best ideas come from your suggestions so we take feedback seriously. If you have an idea or want to make a suggestion please let us know.</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AppthemesMarketplace/~4/hv0YluKFNko\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/plugins/feedpress-for-jobroller/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:7:\"content\";a:3:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n				 \n			 \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:66:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2015/01/feedpress-jr-0.jpg\";s:4:\"type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"600\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"375\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"feedpress-jr-main\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"plain\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n				 \n			 \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:66:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2015/02/feedpress-jr-1.jpg\";s:4:\"type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"600\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"375\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s: