es&#8221;) in the search field.</strong></p>\n<hr />\n<h3>AutoSuggest Features</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Auto-detects services to display to the user based on the characters they&#8217;ve typed.</li>\n<li>Works out of the box; No need for extra settings to be applied.</li>\n<li>Plays nicely with the Taskerr theme and should adapt automatically to custom designs</li>\n</ul>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AppthemesMarketplace/~4/HXKPmylW0pk\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/plugins/autosuggest-taskerr/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:7:\"content\";a:2:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n				 \n			 \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:57:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2015/01/ss-13.png\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"image/png\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"600\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"375\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"ss-1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"plain\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n				 \n			 \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:57:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2015/01/ss-23.png\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"image/png\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"