ed in terms of the search logic.</p>\n<p>AutoSuggest has been engineered to work perfectly with the ClassiPress theme by AppThemes and also includes an automatic style scanner. With the automatic Style Scanner, you&#8217;re able to design your theme (or use a premium child theme from the marketplace) and AutoSuggest should pick up these changes, thereby applying CSS styles the list of suggestions accordingly. In short, AutoSuggest should adapt to your design automatically.</p>\n<p><strong>* To see the demo in action &#8211; start typing a listing name (e.g. &#8220;My First Ad&#8221;) in the field.</strong></p>\n<hr />\n<h3>AutoSuggest Features</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Auto-detects classifieds to display to the user based on the characters they&#8217;ve typed.</li>\n<li>Works out of the box; No need for extra settings to be applied.</li>\n<li>Plays nicely with the ClassiPress theme and should adapt automatically to custom designs and childthemes.</li>\n</ul>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AppthemesMarketplace/~4/KJNk7UgIEiY\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/plugins/autosuggest-classipress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"11\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:7:\"content\";a:2:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n				 \n			 \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:56:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2015/01/ss-1.png\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"image/png\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"600\