ew</h3>\n<p>Auto Location is a premium plugin for JobRoller that uses predictive text via Google Maps to present the user with a list of possible locations based on what has been typed. The aim of this plugin is to enhance user-experience and to make sure that valid locations are selected without any spelling mistakes. On the demo page, type something in the location bar &#8211; you should be presented with a dynamically generated list of options.</p>\n<p>Auto Location also comes with an automatic style scanner &#8211; this means that if our plugin is used with a custom design (or a premium child theme), it should pick up the layout / colours and adapt the suggestion list automatically.</p>\n<p><strong>* To see the demo in action &#8211; start typing a location name (e.g. &#8220;New York&#8221;) in the search field.</strong></p>\n<div class=\"widget boxshadow\">\n<h3>Plugin Requirements</h3>\n<p>For Auto Location to work, you’ll need two things:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A Google Account</li>\n<li>A free Google Maps v3 API key</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you’ve got the account, but not the Google Maps key, please follow the instructions on the plugin settings page.</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AppthemesMarketplace/~4/RarfpPwv154\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/plugins/auto-location-jobroller/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:7:\"content\";a:2:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"