d: #58b35a;border: 1px solid #419f44\" href=\"http://demos.jobthemes.com/index.php=bfinder-default-demo\" target=\"_blank\">Default layout</a> <a class=\"btn green big\" style=\"width: 98%;float: left;margin: 5px;background: #04bad0;border: 1px solid #0692a3\" href=\"http://demos.jobthemes.com/index.php=bfinder-admin\" target=\"_blank\">Admin Demo</a></p>\n<hr style=\"background: none;border: none\" />\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Modern and Clean design:</b> </span>Bfinder has a very fast and clean UI and design. It provides a very user-friendly design which results in a great user-experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Responsive layout:</b></span> It has a responsive layout compatible with all devices. Try it yourself, while browsing the theme’s demo resize the window to see how it automatically adapts.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>4 Home page layouts:</b></span> Choose how you want the home page to display. <strong>Default layout</strong>: the same as in vantage theme, Or ,<strong>Columns layout</strong>: Display the listings in 2 columns, Or, <strong>Tabs layout:</strong> Display the listings on a tabbed view , Or, <strong>Categories layout</strong>: Display the categories and sub categories in a clean grid view. For each layout there are options in the admin to adjust the way you want.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>2 Primary menu styles: </b></span>Either with or without tabs, choose the style of the menu using the admin option.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Categories images: </b></span>Upload a custom image for each listing category.It&#8217;s an option in the admin.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Blog posts in home page:</b></span> Display the blog posts in a very attractive way in the home page, to ease browsing the tips and news You publish on your website. (There are options to select which post category(ies) to show its posts and how many posts.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Grid/List Mode :</b></span> Bfinder is packed with grid/list view, Yet, you can still set the default mode. It&#8217;s set to grid for a fancy and impact look and feel.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>8 Color schemes: </b></span>It comes with 8 predefined skins and theme options layouts that you may use for different purposes.and unlimited colors ( You can change header background, top bar, footer , font colors,..)</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Unlimited colors: </b></span>You can change colors and styles, and customize your Web site to the last corner. The flexibility nature of Bfinder will let you create Local guides,Directories,Reviews portal with completely different display though they are all built from the same awesome framework.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0a92c5\"><b><span style=\"color: #333333\">Featured slider(Listings/events)</span><span style=\"color: #333333\">:</span> </b> </span>Display a stylish featured slider for listings or events, we have an option for it in the admin.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0a92c5\"><b><span style=\"color: #333333\">Revslider included (All updated)</span><span style=\"color: #333333\">:</span> </b></span>We have packed Bfinder with the famous sliders plugin, It&#8217;s made easy to embed your web site directory with a fresh and shining slider.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Easy &amp; Extensive Theme Options:</b> </span> There are tens of options available in the enhanced version of our theme panel.It makes it very easy and comprehensive toconfigure and modify everything in your site easily. No coding skills required. All come out of the box !</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Weather widget : </b></span>As in our other vantage&#8217;s  child theme (<a title=\"Directory theme\" href=\"http://marketplace.appthemes.com/child-themes/vantage/directory/\" target=\"_blank\">Directory</a>) You can display a weather forecast for any city with various beautiful units and icons and eye pleasing weather status that instantly seeks attention of your visitors.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Advertising module:</b></span> More over than the default Vantage advertising spots, Bfinder is packed with enhanced advertising modules that helps you to turn your site into a hits generator.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Custom styles: </b></span>More customization?, You can add a custom CSS code directly the from admin panel. It allows you to change theme look without editing the core theme files. And what is important, custom CSS rules are stored in database and will be saved after theme update.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Custom jscript: </b></span>There is an option for almost everything, In the admin, You can paste any custom js code and the google analytics tracking code.as easy as one click.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Localisation support: </b></span>Bfinder is ready to be translated into any language you want using the .po/.mo files. It uses the same language pack of Vantage.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Compatible with Vantage 1.3.4+: </b></span>Bfinder is completely compatible with and the functions of the latest version of Vantage.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color: #474747\"><strong>Dedicated support</strong> |</span> We take huge pride in our customer support and how it has differentiated us from the competition.We have a support team located 3 countries in just about every time zone and try our hardest to ensure support responses within 24 hours. <span style=\"color: #474747\"><b>Suggestions and Feedback | </b></span>Our best ideas come from your suggestions so we take feedback seriously. If you have an idea or want to make a suggestion please let us know.</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AppthemesMarketplace/~4/i0XQ_5v2dTM\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/child-themes/vantage/bfinder/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"71\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:7:\"content\";a:2:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n				 \n			 \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:64:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2015/01/bfinder-homy.jpg\";s:4:\"type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"600\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"375\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"bfinder-homy\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"plain\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n				 \n			 \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:63:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2015/01/bfinder-big.jpg\";s:4:\"type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"600\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"375\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"bfinder-big\";s:7:\"attrib