;Register&#8217; link will not be shown to website visitors.</li>\n<li>If an administrator logins in, the widget will show a link for the WordPress administrator area. Non-admin users will not have this link (given they won&#8217;t have access).</li>\n<li>Logged in users will get a link to their Dashboard (their listings, favorites, profile etc).</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"padding-left: 30px\">Display user avatars</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>The plugin provides an option to display user avatars in the Smart Login Widget.</li>\n<li>Avatar functionality can be further enhanced by downloading the free WordPress plugin, <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-user-avatar/\" target=\"_blank\">WP User Avatar</a>. For example, you can then allow users to upload their own avatar (by default the themes will display the default placeholder avatar or the users <a href=\"https://en.gravatar.com\" target=\"_blank\">Gravatar</a> if they have one).</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"padding-left: 30px\">Clean design</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>The plugin provides an option to remove the default login rows at the top of every page.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"padding-left: 30px\">Auto-magically adapts to the Vantage, ClassiPress or HireBee style</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>The widget style will match the Vantage, ClassiPress or HireBee style in use (for example, the &#8216;Theme Color&#8217; selected in the Vantage theme settings).</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"padding-left: 30px\">Fully customisable text</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>All of the widget text can be updated in the settings menu. This makes it super easy to customise the text to suit your audience.</li>\n<li>HTML tags (bolding, font colour etc) can be applied to each of the custom text fields in the settings menu.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">See it in action: check out our demo sites</span><br />\n</span></h2>\n<p><a class=\"btn big blue\" title=\"Vantage theme demo\" href=\"http://www.coders.com.au/demos/vantage/\" target=\"_blank\">Vantage demo</a></p>\n<p><a class=\"btn big blue\" title=\"ClassiPress theme demo\" href=\"http://www.coders.com.au/demos/classipress/\" target=\"_blank\">ClassiPress demo</a></p>\n<p><a class=\"btn big blue\" title=\"HireBee theme demo\" href=\"http://www.coders.com.au/demos/hirebee/\" target=\"_blank\">HireBee demo</a></p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AppthemesMarketplace/~4/SfOS5aaXERM\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/plugins/smart-login-widget/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"18\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:7:\"content\";a:2:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n				 \n			 \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:68:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2014/11/SmartLoginWidget.png\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"image/png\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"600\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"375\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Smart Login Widget\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"plain\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n				 \n			 \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:101:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2014/11/SmartLoginWidget-Vantagetheme-notloggedin-640x4