 with the plugin in the demo</p>\n<p>To login use the<br />\nusername:<strong>demo</strong><br />\nand<br />\npassword:<strong>demo</strong></p>\n<p>and then from the admin bar select Styles HireBee&gt;Customize.If you visit the site and you see it customized already hit ctrl+F5 to refresh.</p>\n<p><strong>the demo is not 100% functional and every hour the changes will be lost</strong></p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AppthemesMarketplace/~4/t8lzsnpn4Gc\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/plugins/styles-for-hirebee/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:7:\"content\";a:3:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n				 \n			 \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:64:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2014/11/create-pages.png\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"image/png\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"600\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"375\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"create-pages\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"plain\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n				 \n			 \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:63:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2014/07/Untitled-21.jpg\";s:4: