of it for you</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Requirements:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Activated BalancedPayments.com Account &#8211; Its easy to <a href=\"https://www.balancedpayments.com/get-started\">sign up</a>. Also, see their <a href=\"https://support.balancedpayments.com/hc/en-us/categories/200144810-Is-Balanced-a-good-fit-\">FAQ</a> to verify you meet their requirements.</li>\n<li>AppThemes Product with <a href=\"http://www.appthemes.com/blog/introducing-payments-for-appthemes-products/\">Payments Support</a>. Escrow support required for escrow feature.</li>\n<li>Balanced Payments is available in limited currencies. Check with their website to verify your currency will work.</li>\n<li>PHP version 5.3 or greater with cURL support.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Pictures shown the plugin being used with HireBee and several other payment gateways (not included).</em></p>\n<p>** NOTE: Credit card processing works with all our themes. Escrow support only works with HireBee at this time. **</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AppthemesMarketplace/~4/wI0fgP9VSkU\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/plugins/payment-gateways/balanced-payments/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"21\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:7:\"content\";a:3:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n				 \n			 \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:74:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2014/10/balanced-payments-main.png\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"image/png\";s:6:\"medium