> and <a href=\"http://goo.gl/OSY3UI\" target=\"_blank\">Taskerr</a>!</li>\n<li><strong>Secure</strong> &#8211; Invoices can only be viewed or downloaded by the site admin or the customer.</li>\n<li><strong>Translation ready</strong> &#8211; POT file included for easy customisation or translation of text.</li>\n<li><strong>Admin</strong> &#8211; View and download invoices from the Orders dashboard.</li>\n<li><strong>Frontend</strong> &#8211; Customers can view and download invoices from their user dashboard.</li>\n<li><strong>Multisite</strong> &#8211; Developed and tested in a multisite environment to ensure WP network compatibility.</li>\n<li><strong>Tax Compliant</strong> &#8211; Invoices are compliant with <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/vat-record-keeping/vat-invoices\">UK full VAT requirements</a>. If you need different/extra information for your country please click on the Support tab for contact details.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a class=\"btn blue big\" href=\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2014/06/Vantage-Invoice-76.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Sample PDF Invoice</a></p>\n<h3>Live Demo</h3>\n<p>A live demo, running Vantage, is available to see the Invoices plugin in action. Log in to the live demo and visit the user dashboard:</p>\n<p><code>Username: <strong>demo</strong><br />\nPassword: <strong>demo</strong><br />\n</code></p>\n<p><a class=\"btn blue big\" href=\"http://demo.nomadcode.net/invoices/dashboard/\">Demo</a></p>\n<p>The Invoices plugin is tested against the latest version of WordPress and the development versions of each theme. Please ensure you have the latest dev version of <a href=\"http://goo.gl/O61LwS\" target=\"_blank\">ClassiPress</a>, <a href=\"http://goo.gl/IhybuA\" target=\"_blank\">Vantage</a>, <a href=\"http://goo.gl/grhQwN\" target=\"_blank\">JobRoller</a> or <a href=\"http://goo.gl/jB68da\" target=\"_blank\">Clipper</a> which can be downloaded from the <a href=\"https://my.appthemes.com/purchases/\">Purchases</a> page of your dashboard.<