et place. You are free to mix ads and links as you please but the total links and links are eleven.</p>\n<p>But that is not all we also included a PHP Ad Stuffer Widget so you can add as many ads you want in all the places where you want widgets, size do not matter. We also included the option to change the size of the widget area and included the option to delete the &#8220;powered by&#8221; link.</p>\n<h3>Features:</h3>\n<p>&#8211;<strong> Maximize your Ad revenue! Show eleven more ads &amp; links on your website!</strong><br />\n&#8211; Easy installation with FTP or WordPress admin in your ClassiPress based website.<br />\n&#8211; No edit in code with update!<br />\n&#8211; Clean &amp; Trusted Code!<br />\n&#8211; No need for Child theme or hire webmaster!<br />\n&#8211; Easy install like turning a key!<br />\n&#8211; Free lifetime Support on <a title=\"AppThemes Forum\" href=\"http://forums.appthemes.com\" target=\"_blank\">AppThemes Forum</a> and Greenhatforum.com<br />\n&#8211; Developed by trusted developer Turnkey Script that developed <a title=\"Ad Stuffer ClassiPress\" href=\"http://marketplace.appthemes.com/plugins/ad-stuffer/\" target=\"_blank\">Ad Stuffer for ClassiPress</a></p>\n<h3>Instructions:</h3>\n<p>Install the Ad Stuffer for Vantage by FTP or from WordPress Admin. Activate Ad Stuffer Vantage from inside the WordPress Admin panel. Put your Adsense, php, iframe or java code inside the Ad Stuffer. You find Ad Stuffer Vantage under settings in your WordPress Admin.</p>\n<h3>Compatible:</h3>\n<p>&#8211; Vantage 1.0 &#8211;  1.3.2+&gt;<br />\n&#8211; WordPress 3.0 &#8211; .3.9+&gt;</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AppthemesMarketplace/~4/jVx-2JzDZ4M\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/plugin