eviews</span>  with wide opportunities and ideas as <strong>Guide restaurants</strong>,<strong> Hotels</strong>, <strong>Trips</strong>, <strong>Services</strong>, <strong>Stores</strong> and much more !</p>\n<p>Directory theme offers a rock solid theme back-end with tons of useful tools and options.</p>\n<p>Check out what our actual customers said about it!<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appthemes.com/cart/?product_id=242\"><br />\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7275\" src=\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2014/05/directory-banner1.jpg\" alt=\"directory-banner\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" /></a></p>\n<p><a class=\"btn green big\" style=\"background: #58b35a;border: 1px solid #419f44\" href=\"http://demos.jobthemes.com/index.php=directory-demo\" target=\"_blank\">Live Demo</a></p>\n<p><a class=\"btn green big\" style=\"background: #58b35a;border: 1px solid #419f44\" href=\"http://demos.jobthemes.com/index.php=directory-styled-demo\" target=\"_blank\">Boxed Layout Demo</a></p>\n<p><a class=\"btn green big\" style=\"background: #04bad0;border: 1px solid #0692a3\" href=\"http://demos.jobthemes.com/index.php=directory-admin\" target=\"_blank\">Admin Demo</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Modern, Clean &amp; Flat design:</b> </span> Directory has a very fast and clean UI and design. It provides a very user-friendly design which results in a great user-experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Responsive layout:</b></span> Directory has a responsive layout compatible with all devices. Try it yourself, while browsing the theme’s demo resize the window to see how it automatically adapts.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Full-width or Boxed:</b></span> You have the possibility to select between 2 layout styles: Full-width or boxed</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Grid/List Mode :</b></span> Directory is packed with grid/list view, Yet, you can still set the default mode. It&#8217;s set to grid for a fancy and impact look and feel.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>8 Color schemes: </b></span>It comes with 8 predefined skins and theme options layouts that you may use for different purposes.and unlimited colors ( You can change header background, top bar, footer , font colors,..)</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Unlimited colors: </b></span>You can change colors and styles, and customize your Web site to the last corner. The flexibility nature of Directory will let you create Local guides,Directories,Reviews portal with completely different display though they are all built from the same awesome framework.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Easy &amp; Extensive Theme Options:</b> </span> It has very easy and comprehensive set of theme options that will help you configure and modify everything in your site easily. No coding skills required. All come out of the box !</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Weather widget : </b></span>You can display a weather forecast for any city with various beautiful units and icons and eye pleasing weather status that instantly seeks attention of your visitors.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0a92c5\"><b><span style=\"color: #333333\">Featured slider(Listings/events)</span> <span style=\"color: #0a92c5\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000\">[new]</span></span> <span style=\"color: #333333\">:</span> </b><b></b> </span>Display a stylish featured slider for listings or events, we have an option for it in the admin.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Advertising module:</b></span> More over than the default Vantage advertising spots, Directory is packed with enhanced advertising modules that helps you to turn your site into a hits generator.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Custom styles: </b></span>You need more customization?, You can add custom CSS directly the from admin panel. It allows you to change theme look without editing core theme files. And what is important, custom CSS rules are stored in database and will be saved after theme update.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Localisation support: </b></span>Directory is ready to be translated into any language you want using the .po/.mo files. It uses the same language pack of Vantage.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333\"><b>Compatible with Vantage 1.4+: </b></span>Directory is completely compatible with and the functions of the latest version of Vantage.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/child-themes/vantage/directory/#reviews\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-10062\" src=\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2014/05/reviews-directory.jpg\" alt=\"reviews-directory\" width=\"600\" height=\"1550\" /></a><span style=\"color: #474747\"><strong>Dedicated support</strong> |</span> We take huge pride in our customer support and how it has differentiated us from the competition.We have a support team located 3 countries in just about every time zone and try our hardest to ensure support responses within 24 hours.</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #474747\"><b>Suggestions and Feedback | </b></span>Our best ideas come from your suggestions so we take feedback seriously. If you have an idea or want to make a suggestion please let us know.</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AppthemesMarketplace/~4/vzNklpNc8KQ\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/child-themes/vantage/directory/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modu