uired. All come out of the box !</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0a92c5\"><b>Grid/List Mode :</b></span> Flatron is packed with grid/list view, Yet, you can still set the default mode. It&#8217;s set to grid for a fancy and impact look and feel.</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0a92c5\"><b>Related ads : </b></span>Display a list of related ads in the ad page. the admin can set how many related ads to display as well.</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0a92c5\"><b>6 Color schemes: </b></span>It comes with 6 predefined skins and theme options layouts that you may use for different purposes.and unlimited colors ( You can change header background, top bar, footer , font colors,..)</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0a92c5\"><b>Advertising module:</b></span> More over than the default classipress advertising spots, Flaron is packed with enhanced advertising modules that helps you to turn your site into a hits generator.</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0a92c5\"><b>Custom styles: </b></span>You need more customization?, You can add custom CSS directly the from admin panel. It allows you to change theme look without editing core theme files. And what is important, custom CSS rules are stored in database and will be saved after theme update.</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0a92c5\"><b><span style=\"color: #0a92c5\">Localisation support:</span> </b></span>Flatron is ready to be translated into any language you want using the .po/.mo files. It uses the same language pack of classipress.</li>\n<li><b><span style=\"color: #0a92c5\">Compatible with ClassiPress 3.3.3+:</span> </b>Flaron is completely compatible with and the functions of ClassiPress 3.3.3+</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #474747\"><strong>Dedicated support</strong> |</span> We take huge pride in our customer support and how it has differentiated us from the competition.We have a support team located 3 countries in just about every time zone and try our hardest to ensure support responses within 24 hours.</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #474747\"><b>Suggestions and Feedback | </b></span>Our best ideas come from your suggestions so we take feedback seriously. If you have an idea or want to make a suggestion please let us know.</li>\n</ul>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AppthemesMarketplace/~4/RRG3Zvj4I9E\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/child-themes/classipress/flatron/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"179\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:7:\"content\";a:3:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n				 \n			 \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:72:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2014/03/flatron-screenshot-1.jpg\";s:4:\"type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"600\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"375\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"flatron-screenshot-1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"plain\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n				 \n			 \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:73:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2014/03/flatron-screenshot-14.jpg\";s:4:\"type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"600\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"375\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";