li>\n<li>Job Lister Dashboard</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Resumes Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Ajax autocomplete search in Resumes</li>\n<li>Online Counter of the active Resumes</li>\n<li>Use JobRoller Resumes visibility options</li>\n<li>Redirects to Login if necessary</li>\n<li>Resume contact details interacts with Phone( Telephone ,Number and Email)</li>\n<li>Job Seeker Dashboard</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Notes</h2>\n<p><strong>In this Initial Release version will not be possible to submit Jobs or Resumes trough the mobile phone.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>As an temporary alternative, you can also switch to the desktop version in order to submit Jobs or Resumes.</strong></p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AppthemesMarketplace/~4/UQMcG7MfxXQ\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/plugins/job-board-mobile/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"74\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:7:\"content\";a:3:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n				 \n			 \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:65:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2013/09/teste_005_001.jpg\";s:4:\"type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"600\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"440\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"teste_005_001\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s: