"_blank\">TwinPress Classifieds</a>&#8216;</p>\n<p><strong>Purchasing here will save you over 20% of the cost of purchasing each theme individually</strong></p>\n<p><strong>This bundle has been created to run as a network</strong><br />\nRun multiple AppThemes side-by-side using the <a href=\"http://codex.wordpress.org/Create_A_Network\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress network</a> interface.</p>\n<p>These child-themes have been created using the same design and we have inserted a new menu at the top of the page to allow the customer to easily switch between themes.</p>\n<p>We have pre-built the themes with two color schemes that you may select from, and with a little knowledge of CSS you may create your own swatches (or you could ask us nicely to create one for you).</p>\n<h3>Features</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Clean and responsive design.</li>\n<li>Multisite ready.</li>\n<li>Content has been designed at 1140px to accommodate larger screens.</li>\n<li>Newly formatted Classipress featured slider (no more errors when resizing).</li>\n<li>New top menu for navigation between sites.</li>\n<li>Newly formatted login now integrated as part of each theme.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Excellent support</h3>\n<p>Let us know what you think of our themes and what we could do to improve them. We&#8217;re in this for the long haul and will be pushing out free updates to all purchasers.</p>\n<p><strong>TwinPress Classifieds compatible with:</strong><br />\nClassiPress: v3.3<br />\nWordPress: v3.5.2</p>\n<p><strong>TwinPress Directory compatible with:</strong><br />\nVantage: v1.2.1<br />\nWordPress: v3.5.x</p>\n<p><strong>Please note:</strong> These are child-themes only and will require an AppThemes license for Vantage and ClassiPress.</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AppthemesMarketplace/~4/Dd_YMpEdhRc\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\"