olor: #3366ff\">Version 2.0 is here!!</span></h2>\n<p>(Please note this only works with the &#8220;<strong>Vantage</strong>&#8221; Apptheme)</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #3366ff;font-weight: normal\">Tired of clicking the pagination box and waiting for pages to load? Not anymore with the new Vantage Infinite Scroll Plugin!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #3366ff;font-weight: normal\">Your users can now scroll through paginated pages seamlessly and effortlessly on Search, Category and the User Dashboard without ever having to load a new page! </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2013/03/vantage-infinite-scoll-41.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3226\" src=\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2013/03/vantage-infinite-scoll-41.jpg\" alt=\"vantage-infinite-scoll-4\" width=\"400\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Plugin Includes:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Multiple GIF loading options</li>\n<li>Admin settings page to control various configurations</li>\n<li>No configurations needed…works right out of the box!</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span style=\"color: #3366ff\">Version 2.0 includes:</span></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Faster load times</li>\n<li>Admin can choice Manual Mode (see images below)</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000\">Replace this:</span></strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2013/03/vantage-infinite-scroll-1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3220\" style=\"border: 2px solid #DDD\" src=\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2013/03/vantage-infinite-scroll-1.jpg\" alt=\"vantage-infinite-scroll-1\" width=\"640\" height=\"400\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000\">With this (Auto):</span></strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2013/03/vantage-infinite-scroll-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3221\" style=\"border: 2px solid #DDD\" src=\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2013/03/vantage-infinite-scroll-2.jpg\" alt=\