eed can be approved and submitted, and here Job Feed Generator creates a well formatted xml feed with the latest jobs from your site that you can submit to Indeed.</p>\n<p>Using Job Feed Generator, You can add your site’s jobs to Indeed, the #1 job site worldwide, with over 80 million unique visitors and 1.5 billion job searches per month and available in more than 50 countries and 26 languages.</p>\n<h3>Key Features:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Using Job Feed Generator, You can smoothly submit your jobs to Indeed, the most famous job search engine.</li>\n<li>Your jobs&#8217; feeds will be well formatted to be included in Indeed database for relevant advanced searching tools.</li>\n<li>Use the fastest way to include your jobs to Indeed.</li>\n<li>Receive thousands of job seekers that are browsing Indeed to find a job.</li>\n<li>Promote your job board and increase the number of its visitors.</li>\n<li>Win after the traffic of Indeed.</li>\n<li>Update automatically the last jobs once they are posted to your site.</li>\n<li>The best, it’s free from Indeed to add your jobs to such big search engine.</li>\n<li>Easy to use, install and activate.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Feed Generator is designed with flexibility, ease of use, and ease of configuration in mind.</p>\n<div class=\"box-content\" style=\"background-color: #fff !important\">\n<p><b>To read:</b> Indeed conditions: <a href=\"https://ads.indeed.com/includejobs\" target=\"_blank\">https://ads.indeed.com/includejobs</a><br />\n<b>Covered by the plugin:</b> The xml format and instructions: <a href=\"http://www.indeed.com/intl/en/xmlinfo.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.indeed.com/intl/en/xmlinfo.html</a></p>\n<div class=\"box-frame box-support\">\n<div class=\"box-content\" style=\"background-color: #fff !important\"><span style=\"color: #555;font-weight: normal\">If you need support, feel free to contact us at contact@jobthemes.com, or use the AppThemes support forums.<br />\n</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<img src=\"http://feed