g/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"spartac\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6564:\"<h3>Overview:</h3>\n<p><b>Simplux is super premium Jobroller child theme. </b>It comes with clean &amp; modern design. Simplux is the first premium Jobroller child theme that uses separate theme options panel for fully control of everything in the website. Simplux is an incredibly powerful, super flexible theme, packed with tons of features and options and enhanced with well-studied ad areas to monetize your website. Easy to customize via theme option to have a unique look &amp; feel. All this and more make Simplux the perfect choice for <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">HR professionals</span>, <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Agencies</span>, <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">companies</span>, <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">bloggers</span> and <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">niche hunters</span> that they are looking to market themselves and rise above competition. <a class=\"btn green big\" style=\"background: #dd112a;border: 1px solid #d00820\" href=\"http://demos.jobthemes.com/index.php=simplux-demo\" target=\"_blank\">Live Demo</a> <a class=\"btn green big\" style=\"background: #04bad0;border: 1px solid #0692a3\" href=\"http://demos.jobthemes.com/index.php=simplux-admin\" target=\"_blank\">Admin Demo</a></p>\n<table border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 0px !important;padding: 5px\"><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/jobthemes\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.jobthemes.com/buttons/like-facebook.jpg\" alt=\"Like us on Facebook\" /></a></td>\n<td style=\"border: 0px !important;padding: 5px\"><a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/jobthemes\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.jobthemes.com/buttons/follow-twitter.jpg\" alt=\"Follow us on Twitter\" /> </a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 0px !important;padding: 5px\"><a href=\"http://www.jobthemes.com/live-support/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.jobthemes.com/buttons/online-support.jpg\" alt=\"Live Support\" /></a></td>\n<td style=\"border: 0px !important;padding: 5px\"><a href=\"http://marketplace.appthemes.com/child-themes/jobroller/simplux/#reviews\"><img src=\"http://www.jobthemes.com/buttons/rate-us.jpg\" alt=\"Rate us\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>Key Features:</h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000\"><strong>1- Design :</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Modern &amp; Clean design</li>\n<li>Multiple Color options</li>\n<li>Fixed and centered width.</li>\n<li>Bundled with 5 Preset Skins + 1 default</li>\n<li>Unlimited color schemes using the theme options panel</li>\n<li>Custom backgrounds</li>\n<li>Upload Images to use as background and control the repetition, and its image attachment,</li>\n<li>42 Patterns ready to use. (Change the look of your site with one click)</li>\n<li>Dynamic carrousel (Custom Widget to add logos in the landing area in the header)</li>\n<li>Integrated google fonts (Use variant of google fonts for titles and body text)</li>\n<li>Designed search engine (radius ,inputs and button).</li>\n<li>Share the job to facebook.(integrated in the job listing blocks)</li>\n<li>Well structured home page (It displays tons of content while at the same time it avoids the feeling of clutter.)</li>\n<li>Well designed and organized home page (It displays tons of content while at the same time it avoids the feeling of clutter.)</li>\n<li>Cufon Integrated.</li>\n<li>Full-width (No sidebar) page template created.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000\"><strong>2- </strong><b>Functions</b></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Themes options.</li>\n<li>Ad Management (monetize your website.)</li>\n<li>Theme is fully localized to allow translation into any other language</li>\n<li>Unlimited  colors (Customizable Color via Color Picker)</li>\n<li>Google map including all jobs in the site.</li>\n<li>Custom widgets (Search, Login,..)</li>\n<li>Widgetized Footer (3 areas or 2 or 1 or no area, depends on what you want)</li>\n<li>Three Custom menus, top, primary and footer (Fully control of the navigation menus of your web site)</li>\n<li>Grid/List preview of Job blocks</li>\n<li>Custom CSS (You don’t need to edit core theme files anymore ,</li>\n<li>Fully styled typography</li>\n<li>Compatibility (IE8, Firefox, Safari, Chrome)</li>\n<li>New Custom Taxonomy for Location (City, State or Country)</li>\n<li>Browse by location.</li>\n<li>New custom template for the location taxonomy</li>\n<li>SEO ready to index jobs by location in google</li>\n<li>Control the tabs of the home page using the theme options (the tabs, their order and titles)</li>\n<li>Search-Engine Optimized</li>\n<li>Job listing excerpt.</li>\n<li>It supports all JobRoller features (Compatible and Tested with JR 1.6.4/1.6.5)</li>\n<li>Easy jobs navigation by using well organized blocks.</li>\n<li>Thumbnails integrated in the blocks (recruiter’s logos).</li>\n<li>Insert google adsense between job blocks (This increases the rate of clicks)</li>\n<li>5 Special ad areas to monetize your site (header, footer, home page,job listings and job page)</li>\n<li>Login using username or email.</li>\n<li>New custom fields for registration form (first name, last name,phone,..)</li>\n<li>Switch options between job seeker and job listers loging forms ( Additional fields for companies)</li>\n<li>The news fields being registred in database and displayed in profil and edit profile pages</li>\n<li>Personalized login page ( through the options panel, You can customize the login page elements, add html codes, lists, graphics ect )</li>\n<li>Permanent login form in sidebar</li>\n<li>Customize home page, using html codes under the menu ( adding texts, images , anything 