ch is a premium plugin for JobRoller, it creates widgets that can be displayed in any sidebar on your website which shows a combination of the custom taxonomies and category.</p>\n<p>The plugin allow you to place refine search for jobs or for resumes in any widget area, to help the visitors of your web site to find exactly and quickly what they are looking for (Jobs or Resumes) by keywords and choosing terms from drop down boxes.<br />\nThis plugin makes the search experience a funny smooth experience to your job board visitors.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn green big\" href=\"http://demos.jobthemes.com/index.php=job-super-search-demo\" target=\"_blank\">Live Demo</a></p>\n<h3>Key Features:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Job Super Search plugin lets you place search widgets (Jobs or Resumes) in any sidebar of your web site.</li>\n<li>Two widgets in one plugin ( advanced search for jobs and advanced search for resumes ).</li>\n<li>Refine search engine will be available for visitors to use to find exactly what they are looking for.</li>\n<li>The admin can select the fields he wants to hide or show to the visitors.</li>\n<li>Show/hide the search by keyword.</li>\n<li>Filter the sites by custom taxonomies ( the standard build-in taxonomies and any new ones )</li>\n<li>It shows a combination of your custom taxonomies and category.</li>\n<li>It allows visitors to search within specific categories, or types or salaries or tags as well (ex: Project manager in the category “Administration”).</li>\n<li>Besides searching by keywords, the visitor can combine many terms together.</li>\n<li>Filter job and resumes by custom taxonomies in the admin.</li>\n<li>Sort jobs by custom taxonomies</li>\n<li>Any new custom taxonomy created will be automatically added to the list.</li>\n<li>Translation ready using jobroller .po file.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"box-frame box-support\">\n<div class=\"box-content\" style=\"background-color: #fff !important\"><span style=\"color: #555;font-weight: normal\">If you need support, feel free to contact us at contact@jobthemes.com, or use the AppThemes support forums.<br />\n</span></div>\n</div>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AppthemesMarketplace/~4/gs0rwJv511Q\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/plugins/job-super-search/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"87\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:7:\"content\";a:3:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n				 \n			 \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:73:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2012/10/jobright-screenshot-0.jpg\";s:4:\"type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"600\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"375\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"jobright-screenshot-0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"plain\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n				 \n			 \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:74:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/files/2012/10/jobright-screenshot-14.jpg\";s:4:\"type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"600\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"375\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.y