</li>\n<li>Use the Stripe modal window <a href=\"https://stripe.com/checkout\" target=\"_blank\">checkout process</a> for a more professional checkout experience. <strong><em>(NEW in version 1.1)</em></strong></li>\n<li>Accept Payments from Visa, MasterCard, American Express, Discover, JCB and Diners Club cards.</li>\n<li>Stripe handles the processing, transmission, and storage of credit card data so you don&#8217;t need to worry about PCI compliance.</li>\n<li>Utilizes <a href=\"https://stripe.com/checkout\">Stripe Checkout</a> for easy payments for return customers.</li>\n<li>SSL support for sites with certificates</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Requirements:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Activated Stripe.com Account &#8211; Its easy to <a href=\"https://manage.stripe.com/register\">sign up</a>. Also, see their <a href=\"https://stripe.com/us/help/faq#who-should-not-use-stripe\">FAQ</a> to verify you meet their requirements.</li>\n<li>AppThemes Product with <a href=\"http://www.appthemes.com/blog/introducing-payments-for-appthemes-products/\">Payments Support</a>.</li>\n<li>Stripe is available in limited currencies. Check with their website to verify your currency will work.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Pictures shown the plugin being used with Vantage (not included).</em></p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AppthemesMarketplace/~4/IHOXtDQ8x1I\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://marketplace.appthemes.com/plugins/payment-gateways/stripe/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"80\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"